events.name: Info Session on the GDG
events.description:
We'll get to know -

1. Why GDG and what you stand to gain as a member of the GDG community

2. What the GDG stands for, the opportunities etc.

3. The technologies and how you can leverage on the for your professional growth.

4. Panel and workshop sessions and more.

upcoming.name: Amp Study Jam
upcoming.description:
We'll be having hands-on workshop series on AMP which is an open-source HTML framework created by Google that provides a straightforward way to create web pages that are fast, smooth-loading and prioritize the user-experience above all else.

We'll be deploying our completed project too!! Newbies are most welcome.

Who should attend?
AMP Study Jam is suited best for:
1) those just getting started with modern web development
2) those with programming experience in other JavaScript frameworks

NOTE: Venue would be announced.

upcoming.name: WTM Owerri celebrates her IWD(International Women's Day)
upcoming.description:
*International Women's Day 2020 campaign theme is #EachforEqual*

An equal world is an enabled world.

Individually, we're all responsible for our own thoughts and actions - all day, every day.

We can actively choose to challenge stereotypes, fight bias, broaden perceptions, improve situations and celebrate women's achievements.

Collectively, each one of us can help create a gender equal world.

EachforEqual

group_profile.intro: A software engineer, community builder, as well as an advocate for women inclusion in tech.
